{"tid":1385612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要自設門檻，五大訴求唔係缺一不可咩?","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:10:35.000Z","uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13bd333b86712649427562845c49e38bed7ee026","tid":1385612,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"而家政府唔鳩理你，你就話只要一樣野，集中訴求?<br />\n從一開始就係五樣野都要爭取，然後而家有啲唔知咩人話爭取獨立調查委員會/ 雙普選二揀一<br />\n之後爭取愈嚟愈多方便文宣，因為有晒理據<br />\n加多樣警黑勾結都重得<br />\n咁係咪爭取到雙普選就唔洗要其他嗰幾樣?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好唔記得從來都係我地拋個波出嚟要政府回應</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢唔回你，你就要自閹只提一樣?<br />\n係應該叫晒咁多樣迫佢回應啊嘛"},{"pid":"e5a4caa064e4ad2eb13b76b3a307012aed8a7326","tid":1385612,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"推到政府回應"},{"pid":"3d06ce59a873d686030e7ef2121cab90e012bf04","tid":1385612,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"推到政府回應"},{"pid":"a5718560c904b08e04aa6e8f9954ffa2f03b57f4","tid":1385612,"uid":164938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:35:01.000Z","msg":"Fact checked<br />\n明天機場博覽館要人！！<br />\n7.31<br />\n16:00-17:30<br />\n機場Asia World Expo-Summit 2號展館<br />\n政府開pre policy address meeting! <br />\n會議是為運輸及貿易界而設既諮詢會，將有好多公司出席！<br />\n<br />\n聽日7.31機場博覽館要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385635</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0dd514c5f92bd3353f1f8170d56ac05b66218661","tid":1385612,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"推到政府回應"},{"pid":"b9e5923a0dab2c6bab6d5165668630e5ceafdc3c","tid":1385612,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"推到政府回應"},{"pid":"999852dcbb3b05920914e8e67c5af59bb2ab83fc","tid":1385612,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit